Smusher 11-Apr-21 01:41 PM
War declaration format: (Your faction name) vs (Enemy name) - Declaration of war Write anything you want here. The terms of the war and who is recording/spectating. Whoever is spectating the war can change them. After that, get a war spectator to talk with you and the opposing faction about what time, allies, prize if you win, and anything else you want to discuss. The war spectator will watch the war and record the war and will decide who wins. After the war is over, the winner will get whatever was in the terms. This channel is only for the one message and the opposing faction's leader to agree or disagree. Any other chatting can be done in a group chat (with the war spectator) or in #》faction-discussion Please ping the opposing faction reps and a war spectator in your war declaration. (edited)
